    job_description:
      "Job Title: ReactJS Developer\n\nJob Description:\n\nWe are looking for a skilled ReactJS Developer to join our dynamic team. As a ReactJS Developer, you will be responsible for developing and implementing user interface components using React.js, and you should be well-versed in various web development tools and technologies. If you have expertise in Figma to App conversion, Azure Cosmos DB, Azure DevOps, and AI Application Development, you'll find exciting opportunities to apply your skills in our projects.\n\nResponsibilities:\n\n1. Develop new user-facing features using React.js.\n\n2. Build reusable components and front-end libraries for future use.\n\n3. Translate designs and wireframes into high-quality code.\n\n4. Optimize components for maximum performance across various web-capable devices and browsers.\n\n5. Collaborate with other team members and stakeholders to deliver outstanding user experiences.\n\n6. Participate in code reviews and contribute to maintaining high code quality standards.\n\nRequirements:\n\n1. Strong proficiency in JavaScript, including DOM manipulation and the JavaScript object model.\n\n2. Thorough understanding of React.js and its core principles.\n\n3. Experience with popular React.js workflows (such as Flux or Redux).\n\n4. Familiarity with newer specifications of EcmaScript.\n\n5. Experience with data structure libraries (e.g., Immutable.js).\n\n6. Knowledge of isomorphic React is a plus.\n\n7. Familiarity with RESTful APIs.\n\n8. Experience with common front-end development tools such as Babel, Webpack, NPM, etc.\n\n9. Ability to understand business requirements and translate them into technical requirements.\n\n10. A knack for benchmarking and optimization.\n\n11. Familiarity with code versioning tools such as Git, SVN, or Mercurial.\n\n12. Excellent communication skills and a team-oriented mindset.\n\nAdditional Skills (Preferred):\n\n1. Experience with Figma to App development.\n\n2. Proficiency in working with Azure Cosmos DB.\n\n3. Familiarity with Azure DevOps for project management and collaboration.\n\n4. Knowledge of AI Application Development.\n\nApplication Process:\n\nPlease submit your resume along with a portfolio showcasing your work, especially projects completed using ReactJS. Include brief descriptions of your role and contributions in these projects. Your expertise in Figma to App conversion, Azure Cosmos DB, Azure DevOps, and AI Application Development will be a valuable asset to our team.",
